[1mBUGS[0m
       Occasionally  [4mRog-O-Matic[24m  will dead-lock waiting for input from [4mRogue.[0m
       When this happens, type an interrupt and enter  the  [4mt[24m  command  again.
       This  usually  wakes  it up enough to re-start the game.  In completely
       unusual cases, try interrupting and then entering the [4mS[24m command to save
       the game, and then re-start with "rogomatic  -r".  Sometimes  you  will
       have  to  use  transparent mode to get it down to the next level before
       turning it loose again.

